data.text:
Frawls, Burkey & Moss review Round 1 of the Energia AIL action, and preview Round 2. Moss rounds up the first week of Ace of Clubs, with Walter Lyons leading the way.

Stephen Keogh & Lee Nicholas from Shannon RFC join us to discuss their victory over UCD, and the upcoming derby versus Young Munster.

Powered by Energia #PositiveEnergy
